\par <#/>}{\fs24\lang2057 The Tutsi and Hutu make up the Burundian people. <#/>However, while the Tutsi are semi-hermitic the Hutus are Bantu. <#/>The Hutu constitute the majority of the Burundi population but the Tutsi are the minority.
